{"tid":269481,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[消滅中共和中國霸權]李登輝之台灣的主張和新台灣主張著作","createTime":"2017-06-03T18:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T04:55:48.000Z","uid":100986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9af95d69901d05675af12df3a4364fe88fa6afd","tid":269481,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:30:17.000Z","msg":"[消滅中共和中國霸權]李登輝之台灣的主張和新台灣主張著作(日文版同中文版)<br />\n<br />\n台湾の主張 単行本 &ndash; 1999/6<br />\n李 登輝  (著)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/LlDSDGi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLlDSDGi.jpg&h=5c1e007d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/台湾の主張-李-登輝/dp/4569606407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2F%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE%E3%81%AE%E4%B8%BB%E5%BC%B5-%E6%9D%8E-%E7%99%BB%E8%BC%9D%2Fdp%2F4569606407&d=UvprCxjRFPMsPvJ3PrIHF%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=8e206673\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.jp/台湾の主張-李-登輝/dp/4569606407</a><br />\n<br />\n新・台湾の主張 (PHP新書) 新書 &ndash; 2015/1/16<br />\n李 登輝  (著)<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/B8HZxfMCYAAL4jl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FB8HZxfMCYAAL4jl.jpg&h=113f1716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/新・台湾の主張-PHP新書-李-登輝/dp/4569823645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2F%E6%96%B0%E3%83%BB%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE%E3%81%AE%E4%B8%BB%E5%BC%B5-PHP%E6%96%B0%E6%9B%B8-%E6%9D%8E-%E7%99%BB%E8%BC%9D%2Fdp%2F4569823645&d=UvprCxjRFPMsPvJ3PrIHF%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f0b11ec1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.jp/新・台湾の主張-PHP新書-李-登輝/dp/4569823645</a>"},{"pid":"73fb6102a8c71b408497e4fb88865c73925d2cf7","tid":269481,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:34:29.000Z","msg":"<strong>打臉洪秀柱？日本駐台代表：我就是狗的代表</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpVmoxTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpVmoxTa.jpg&h=b5cb18ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前總統李登輝發表新書《新台灣的主張》，暢談著作理念。（記者劉信德攝）<br />\n<br />\n2015-09-15<br />\n<br />\n〔記者陳慧萍／台北報導〕前總統李登輝在新書《新台灣的主張》中引述「狗去豬來」的民間說法，稱台灣人感嘆「戰前統治台灣的日本人是狗，來自大陸的中國人則是豬」，國民黨總統參選人洪秀柱批評李登輝以「豬」稱呼特定群體，令人遺憾；不過日本駐台代表沼田幹夫今天出席李登輝新書發表會時，自我介紹說「所謂『狗去豬來』，我就是狗的代表」，大方面對這段歷史，絲毫不以為忤。<br />\n<br />\n日本交流協會代表沼田幹夫今天下午出席李登輝《新台灣的主張》新書發表會時，全程以中文致詞。他感謝李登輝今年7月訪日對於日本東北地震的關懷，並推崇李登輝是亞洲偉大的政治家，能出席新書發表會，至感榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n沼田表示，他認同李登輝提到台灣與日本都重視人權與和平；在他記憶裡，亞洲偉大的政治家除了蔣介石、尼赫盧及李光耀外，現在的李登輝絕對是偉大的政治家；他說，為了東亞的安定、和平，日本與台灣一定要一同邁步前進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpmiyR12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpmiyR12.jpg&h=851cdc66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前總統李登輝發表新書《新台灣的主張》，暢談著作理念。（記者劉信德攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1445569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F1445569&d=UvprCxjRFPMsPvJ3PrIHF%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=abbeee68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F1445569&h=059d9928\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1445569</a>"},{"pid":"12296a304458f600807db58b1850881cb2721a14","tid":269481,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016750f7c31b3f665df67cb6ff6ab802fbb5a2d6","tid":269481,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:40:14.000Z","msg":"李登輝係華獨(台灣已經獨立，因中華民國已經台灣化)"},{"pid":"73a4a4edfd593c9ad78f41974ea6ba627838238f","tid":269481,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:46:58.000Z","msg":"